CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 2, 1962, pg. 1, reads: "Camrbia County was well represented at the affair. Left to right are Burrell Hazelrig, secretary for Western Pennsylvania Republican Committee, Mr. Scranton, Raymond Hemphill and Robert A. Gleason, Cambria County Chairman... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Burrell Hazelrig, Pennsylvania gubernatorial candidate William "Bill" Scranton, Raymond Hemphill and Robert A. Gleason, gathered for Republican banquet, Loendi Club
